      <title>马杜罗提议改革允许腐败分子判处无期徒刑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/maduro-proposes-reform-allowing-life-sentences-for-corruption</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗提议进行宪法改革，允许对被判犯有腐败和叛国罪的人判处无期徒刑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/maduro-proposes-reform-allowing-life-sentences-for-corruption</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 21:42:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着中东进入危险的新阶段，以色列受到伊朗的攻击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/israel-says-it-s-under-attack-by-iranian-drones-as-risk-surges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗向以色列发射了攻击无人机和导弹，显然是对叙利亚袭击造成伊朗高级军官死亡的报复，这可能是一次史无前例的袭击，增加了更广泛地区冲突的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/israel-says-it-s-under-attack-by-iranian-drones-as-risk-surges</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 20:55:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列国防军发言人称，伊朗已向以色列发射无人机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/iran-has-launched-drones-toward-israel-idf-spokesperson-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列军方发言人周六表示，伊朗已向以色列发射无人机。]]></description>
